    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090800/extras/e1529f2dc122aec97465680776385a71.avif?t=1735289916\" width=460 height=270 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090800/extras/ad10bbbf0c6097db80d99659f63dcc38.poster.avif?t=1735289916\" width=460 height=52 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090800/extras/ad10bbbf0c6097db80d99659f63dcc38.webm?t=1735289916\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090800/extras/ad10bbbf0c6097db80d99659f63dcc38.mp4?t=1735289916\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Experience a summer filled with danger and romance!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090800/extras/ed4086e4fba2881f0bc83629fb62d007.poster.avif?t=1735289916\" width=460 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090800/extras/ed4086e4fba2881f0bc83629fb62d007.webm?t=1735289916\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090800/extras/ed4086e4fba2881f0bc83629fb62d007.mp4?t=1735289916\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in a romantic and detective adventure alongside Hikari in the picturesque Japanese town surrounded by the mysterious Ancient Forest. Can you help Hikari solve the <u>crime</u> and navigate the storm of her romantic <u>feelings</u>?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will it be the enigmatic stranger or the sweet classmate? Love or fear? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make decisions wisely, as every action can profoundly alter Hikari's fate.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock all 6 (six) endings and experience unforgettable <u>emotions!</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Captivating detective storyline.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >First love and romance.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6 (six) unique endings.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unbelievable mysteries.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Beautiful atmospheric music.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Charming characters and scenic backgrounds.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Includes a roadmap to unlock all endings.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An unforgettable summer adventure!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>This game is not suitable for children or those who are easily disturbed.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Another visual novel: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
